nd/tests/test_model_usage_service.py:129:        assert composition_bucket.token_usage.total_tokens == 2800\nbackend/tests/test_model_usage_service.py:130:        assert composition_bucket.last_model_id == \"gemini-3.1-pro\"\nfrontend/src/shared/ui/primitives.test.tsx:85:        <StackedListItem>Beat sheet</StackedListItem>\nfrontend/src/shared/ui/primitives.test.tsx:91:    expect(screen.getByText('Beat sheet')).toBeInTheDocument()\ndocs/bedtime-guidelines.md:69:  `character`, `beat`, `composition`, and `audio`.\ndocs/bedtime-guidelines.md:84:rewrite.\ndocs/bedtime-guidelines.md:110:    stage=\"composition\",\ndocs/bedtime-guidelines.md:116:pipeline step. Composition and audio fragments already exist even though those prompt templates are\nbackend/tests/test_beat_sheet_generation_service.py:192:    assert result.prompt_version == \"beat_sheet_generation.v2\"\nbackend/tests/test_beat_sheet_generation_service.py:215:    assert result.prompt_version == \"beat_sheet_generation.v2\"\nbackend/tests/test_beat_sheet_generation_service.py:240:            summary=\"Existing harbor beat sheet.\",\nbackend/tests/test_beat_sheet_generation_service.py:270:    assert model_output[\"prompt_version\"] == \"beat_sheet_generation.v2\"\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:1:# Segmented Writing Context Carryover\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:3:The composition runtime now treats each outline card as a durable writing segment and carries\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:8:For each segment run, the backend refreshes two context layers:\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:11:   - Re-assembles the composition prompt package for the active outline card.\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:12:   - Pulls the current genre, tone, brief, selected pitch, selected character sheet, beat sheet,\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:13:     story setup, outline card, and continuity bible pointers.\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:16:   - Loads the latest completed segment revision for each earlier segment index.\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:17:   - Extracts a durable `accepted_summary` for each prior segment.\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:21:The runtime stores this carryover under `composition_segments.payload.context_carryover` so later\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:22:rewrites can inspect the exact structured input that was used when a segment was generated.\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:28:- Rewrites do not depend on replaying the entire prior draft verbatim.\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:29:- Segment prompts stay bounded even as the story gets longer.\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:31:- The session can compile the final story from the latest accepted segment revision at each index.\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:33:## Durable Segment Record\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:35:Each `composition_segments` row now stores:\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:37:- `raw_generated_text`: the first-pass generated segment text\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:38:- `accepted_text`: the persisted segment prose used for compilation and later playback/export\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:39:- `accepted_summary`: the compact handoff summary for downstream segments\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:41:- `payload.context_carryover`: the structured prior-segment context that fed this run\ndocs/segmented-writing-context-carryover.md:43:The object-storage side also keeps a `composition_segment` asset per completed segment revision,\nfrontend/src/features/session/catalogQueries.ts:18:    staleTime: 5 * 60_000,\nfrontend/src/features/session/catalogQueries.ts:27:    staleTime: 5 * 60_000,\nfrontend/src/styles/index.css:1082:.plan-revision-panel__composition-note,\nfrontend/src/styles/index.css:2096:.continuity-inspector__list {\nfrontend/src/styles