{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_153","type":"agent_message","text":"I found one subtle downstream leak: some non-composition services still treat “latest revision” as “accepted manuscript,” which is no longer true once pending rewrites exist. I’m correcting the audio-estimate path so it reads only current accepted segment revisions."}}
