ion:3193b0ba-3739-4a74-a1e7-91b1cd456493. Replaying from sequence 1.\n\nIn progress\nReturn home\nChat lane\n\nMessages, action echoes, and redirect notes stay visible beside the structured workflow.\n\nLive feed connected\n\nReady for notes, approvals, and stage edits from the conversation lane.\n\nAssistant\nApr 2, 6:53 PM\n\nWriting update 33% (1/2): Pip stays close enough to steady every surprise... Direction: Opening Image keeps.... Focus: Move from opening....\n\nAssistant\nApr 2, 6:53 PM\n\nSegment 1/2 handoff: The moment lands in calm repair, so Mira and Pip... Direction: Opening Image keeps.... Focus: Move from opening....\n\nAssistant\nApr 2, 6:53 PM\n\nWriting update 36% (1/2): Additional guidance: Let each chapter land calmer... Direction: Opening Image keeps.... Focus: Move from opening....\n\nAssistant\nApr 2, 6:56 PM\n\nWriting update 33% (1/2): Pip stays close enough to steady every surprise... Direction: Opening Image keeps.... Focus: Move from opening....\n\nAssistant\nApr 2, 6:56 PM\n\nSegment 1/2 handoff: The moment lands in calm repair, so Mira and Pip... Direction: Opening Image keeps.... Focus: Move from opening....\n\nAssistant\nApr 2, 7:01 PM\n\nWriting update 67% (1/1): Pip stays close enough to steady every surprise... Direction: Opening Image keeps.... Focus: Move from opening....\n\nAssistant\nApr 2, 7:01 PM\n\nSegment 1/1 handoff: The moment lands in calm repair, so Mira and Pip... Direction: Opening Image keeps.... Focus: Move from opening....\n\nMessage composer\n\nSend approvals, nudges, or revision notes without leaving the current workspace stage.\n\nReady\nQuick actions\n\nRun a common action in one tap, or type the slash version.\n\nCommands\nNext stage\nRegenerate pitches\nSummarize plan\n\nSlash commands: /next-stage, /regenerate-pitches, /plan\n\nMessage composer\n\nPress Enter to send. Press Shift+Enter for a new line. Try /next-stage, /regenerate-pitches, /plan.\n\n0/1200 characters\n\nSend message\nWorkflow canvas\n\nThe main pane keeps enough width for forms, stage review, and later composition or audio progress views.\n\nIn progress\nStage navigator\n\nEvery required workflow step is visible now, with URL-backed panel selection that can coexist with backend-owned stage truth.\n\n01\n\nSTAGE 01\n\nGenre\n\nChoose the overall bedtime-story lane before the rest of the plan is shaped.\n\nComplete\nRevisitable\nAvailable stages can mount richer editors later without changing the shell.\n02\n\nSTAGE 02\n\nTone\n\nChoose the emotional texture and bedtime-safety posture for the session.\n\nComplete\nRevisitable\nAvailable stages can mount richer editors later without changing the shell.\n03\n\nSTAGE 03\n\nStory brief\n\nCapture the user's free-form idea and any normalized planning summary derived from it.\n\nComplete\nRevisitable\nAvailable stages can mount richer editors later without changing the shell.\n04\n\nSTAGE 04\n\nPitches\n\nGenerate, compare, refine, and accept candidate story directions.\n\nComplete\nRevisitable\nAvailable stages can mount richer editors later without changing the shell.\n05\n\nSTAGE 05\n\nCharacters\n\nDefine the accepted character sheet that later planning and writing will reference.\n\nComplete\nRevisitable\nAvailable stages can mount richer editors later without changing the shell.\n06\n\nSTAGE 06\n\nBeat sheet\n\nStore the accepted Save-the-Cat beat sheet for the session.\n\nComplete\nRevisitable\nAvailable stages c\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
